  "sn46.47:4.1": "“‘<span class=\\\"var\\\" title=\\\"adaḷiddo adaḷiddoti (bj, s1-3)\\\" id=\\\"note104\\\">Adaliddo, adaliddo’ti</span>, bhante, vuccati.",
